sub_title: Us2.ai - On a mission to make healthcare available to all
summary:
Over 20 year of experience in healthcare and echocardiography.
Obtained a PhD in the field of cardiology, specializing in heart failure, echocardiographic detection of subtle cardiac damage and cardio mechanics. 

Since 2017 co-founder of Us2.ai (www.Us2.ai) and on a mission to automate the fight against heart disease

Specialties: Echocardiography, novel echocardiographic techniques, echocardiographic software, diastolic heart failure, GCP, trials, big data sets, machine learning
